reviewText: Interview is OK, nothing too exciting.  The best part is getting to know Carolla a bit more.  The questions posed by the audience were not miked so it was hard to determine what the question was.  Overall an OK show.
If you ar a Carolla fan, you'll find this this to be a lot of the same material but it is a different forum and was nice to come across. I wasn't even aware he did this.
